Vite, saute !

1017
01:14:29.336 --> 01:14:30.503
Bingo !

1018
01:14:30.837 --> 01:14:32.964
T'as vu ça, Clive ? Anéantis.

1019
01:14:33.423 --> 01:14:35.091
Salut, les frangins.

